    "Now whenDaniel came toknow",
    "that thewritinghad beensigned,",
    "he wentto hishouse inhisupperroom",
    "with his windows opent'ward Jerusalem,",
    "threetimes dailyhe kneltdown andprayed.",
    "He gavethanks beforehisGod",
    "ashe hadalwaysdone so,",
    "he hadalwayskneltdown andprayed.",
    "Danielprayed totheLord",
    "for Hisguidance,",
    "and forGod's ownpurpose."
